<bibRefCitation id="D90A4B6FFFD3FFCAFC555105BB434470" author="Foote, R. H." box="[965,1112,360,382]" pageId="1" pageNumber="216" pagination="66 - 149" refId="ref3736" refString="Foote, R. H. 1984. Family Tephritidae. In: Soos, A., Papp, L., eds. Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera, Vol. 9, Micropezidae - Agromyzidae. Akademiai Kiado &amp; Elsevier Science Publishers, Budapest &amp; Amsterdam, 66 - 149." type="book chapter" year="1984">Foote, 1984: 93</bibRefCitation>
